Bacterium

Bacterium wakes up. He looks around. Everything is so big. He gets up 
to walk to the control panel. Where's the control panel? He looks 
around. Where's Amobeous? Where is evreything. He was probally 
captured. "Transform." Bacterium Transforms to his bot mode. He grows 
to his regular size. "Thats strange. Computer how long have I been 
here."

Computer:4 days, 6 hours, 35 minutes, and 57 seconds.

"I think I get it. What is my beast mode?"

Computer:Ummm, A Bacteria.

"So thats it."
